### ── Register a user ─────────────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "babak",
  "email": "babak@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "passwordConfirm": "password123"
}

###

### ── Login ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
### after login the session cookie is saved automatically
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "babak@example.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### ── Logout ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/logout

###

### ── Public: get all albums (no login needed) ────────────────────
GET http://localhost:3000/api/albums

###

### ── Create album (must be logged in) ───────────────────────────
POST http://localhost:3000/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Dark Side of the Moon",
  "artist": "Pink Floyd",
  "year": 1973,
  "trackCount": 10,
  "genre": "Rock"
}

###

### ── Create album without login (should fail 401) ────────────────
### logout first then try this
POST http://localhost:3000/api/albums
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Unauthorized Album",
  "artist": "No User",
  "year": 2020,
  "trackCount": 5,
  "genre": "Pop"
}

###

### ── Update album (must be logged in, replace id) ────────────────
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/albums/69dba2601bb77fb19090a78e
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Title",
  "artist": "Pink Floyd",
  "year": 1973,
  "trackCount": 10,
  "genre": "Rock"
}

###

### ── Delete album (must be logged in, replace id) ────────────────
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/albums/69dba2601bb77fb19090a78e